title: The money saving deals Apple and Google are hiding from you
description: You can’t buy a Netflix subscription in the app. Audible is cheaper if you don’t pay in the app. Why should this be kept secret from you?

title: The right’s new culture-war target: ‘Woke AI’
description: ChatGPT, Google’s Bard, Microsoft’s Bing and DALL-E are causing the far right to decry “woke AI.”
